<section id="packages-overview" class="copy">
  <h1>Service Packages</h1>
  <p>Every business has different needs so we created different packages to better match what our partners want. </br>Do you need a help maintaining your implementation or do you need dedicated analyst support? Something in between? Regardless, we have a package for you.</p>
  <p>&nbsp;</p>
  <h3>Features on all packages</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>30-day money back guarantee</li>
    <li>Automated billing</li>
    <li>On-demand chat support</li>
  </ul>
</section>
<section id="packages-cards" class="copy">
  <div class="cards">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-image">
        <%= image_tag "package_robot.png" %>
      </div>
      <div class="card-header">
        Monitoring Package
      </div>
      <div class="card-copy">
        <p>The Monitoring Package is for existing digital analytics implementations. We add monitoring for KPIs across all platforms and proactively resolve any issues. Benefits include:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Unlimited fixes and small updates</li>
          <li>Analytics and tag manager management</li>
          <li>Vendor updates as needed</li>
          <li>$895 per month</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-image">
        <%= image_tag "package_concierge.png" %>
      </div>
      <div class="card-header">
        Concierge Package
      </div>
      <div class="card-copy">
        <p>The Concierge Package adds personal service and training so you are able to maintain and improve your digital analytics infrastructure. Benefits include everything in the Monitoring Package plus:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>One training session each month</li>
          <li>Monthly status meetings</li>
          <li>$1,495 per month</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-image">
        <%= image_tag "package_mathematician.png" %>
      </div>
      <div class="card-header">
        Analyst Package
      </div>
      <div class="card-copy">
        <p>The Analyst Package adds an assigned analyst that knows your business. Benefits include everything in the Concierge Package plus:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Create integrated dashboards</li>
          <li>Provide analytics reports and insights</li>
          <li>Data exploration and investigation</li>
          <li>Statistical analysis</li>
          <li>$2,895 per month</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</section>
